This project derives from and is a combined/derivative work of:

  uniden-firmware-tool  —  https://github.com/AngeloD2022/uniden-firmware-tool
  Copyright (C) its authors (@AngeloD2022, @jevinskie), licensed AGPL-3.0.

The firmware container layout and the "old" Sound / GPS-database transform
(the 2-bit-plane transpose + subtract key) originate from that project and are
reimplemented here in Python. AGPL-3.0 is retained for compliance.

Work original to this project: recovery of the code-section subtract keys and
ARM Cortex-M decoding; the display blitter/bitmap formats and boot-logo
location; the LZSS .data decompressor; and the Scan-animation format and tools.

